videos.headline: Carson's 3 keeps WVU close
videos.description: Jasmine Carson knocks down a transition 3-pointer to help West Virginia cut into Georgia Tech's lead.

videos.headline: GT's Fletcher can knock them down from anywhere
videos.description: Kierra Fletcher drains back-to-back jumpers on opposite sides of the court, giving the Yellow Jackets a healthy lead.

videos.headline: Georgia Tech scores on back-to-back hustle plays
videos.description: Lorela Cubaj cleans up a missed bucket and Eylia Love scores off the steal seconds later.
